        void performQuery(ObjectName objectName,
                Object value,
                long epochInMillis,
                Queue<QueryResult> results)
        Parameters:
        objectName - objectName on which the attribute was obtained.
        value - value of the given attribute. A 'simple' value (String, Number, Date) for a QuerySimpleAttribute or a CompositeData for a QueryCompositeAttribute.
        epochInMillis - time at which the metric was collected
        results - queue to which the the computed result(s) must be added
